        </div>
        <div style="padding:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy-dark),var(--navy));border-radius:var(--radius-lg);text-align:center;color:var(--white);margin-top:48px;">
          <h2 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:8px;">Lock In Your Memorial Day Rental</h2>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin-bottom:20px;">Tell us your dates, where you're headed, and how many people. We'll match you to the right vehicle while we still have it.</p>
          <a href="tel:+17153961466" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">
